      <b>
       w r nt cnsmrs
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Thr’s  tndncy, vn mng ths wh r tryng t by lss stff, t cll vryn “cnsmrs”. Th cmpny nds t pls ts cnsmrs … w cnsmrs nd t vt wth r dllrs … w nd wtchdgs t prtct cnsmrs … cnsmrs r byng lss drng th rcssn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Lt’s stp tht. W r nt cnsmrs.
      </p>
      <p>
       W’r ppl.
      </p>
      <p>
       Whn w llw rslvs t b brndd wth ths typs f crprt trms, w’v gvn n t th cnsmrst mndst. W’v llwd th dbt t b frmd rnd byng: shld w by rgnc r lcl? Hw cn w prtct cnsmrs? D cnsmrs hv rghts? Wht’s th bst wy t spnd r mny n prdcts? Hw cn w b svvy cnsmrs? Hw cn w ffct chng n scty by mkng thcl r cnscs byng chcs?
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht bt th qstn f whthr w shld b byng r nt? Tht gts thrwn t th wndw, bcs t’s lrdy ssmd n th trm: w’r cnsmrs. Of crs w by. It’s jst  mttr f hw, hw mch, whr, frm whm, hw ftn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt f w stp thnkng f rslvs s cnsmrs, nd strt cllng rslvs “ppl”, thn w pn p th qstn. Shld w vn by n th frst plc? Is t pssbl t lv  lf wtht byng?
      </p>
      <p>
       W tlkd  bt bt tht n
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/reimagined/">
        scty, rmgnd
       </a>
       … tht w cn grw r wn fd, mk nd trd nd shr vrythng w nd. It’s pssbl — f crs t’s pssbl! Hmn bngs (nt cnsmrs) dd t fr hndrds f thsnds f yrs, nd t lst 10,000 yrs n cvlzd scty: w lvd nd wrkd nd plyd nd lvd, wtht byng. W dd t n trbs, f crs, bt ls n lrgr scts tht wrn’t bsd rnd th bsc nt f crprtn -&gt; cnsmr.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’m nt dvctng  rtrn t trblsm. I’m syng w nd t chng th dbt. W nd t stp cllng rslvs cnsmrs. W nd t pn p r mnds, s tht  dffrnt wy s pssbl.
      </p>
